### ============================================================
### MAPS GEOJSON API - NEW TYPE_MAP IMPLEMENTATION
### ============================================================

### Get all maps
GET http://dev.skj.my.id:82/api/maps
Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_TOKEN}
Accept: application/json

### Get maps filtered by type (JALAN, BLOK, ANCAK)
GET http://dev.skj.my.id:82/api/maps?type_map=JALAN
Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_TOKEN}
Accept: application/json

### Get specific map by ID
GET http://dev.skj.my.id:82/api/maps/1
Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_TOKEN}
Accept: application/json

### Create new map from file upload (JALAN type)
POST http://dev.skj.my.id:82/api/maps
Authorization: Bearer {YOUR_TOKEN}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="geojson"; filename="jalan_mte1_mre5.geojson"
Content-Type: application/json

< C:\Users\ridwa\Downloads\jalan_mte1_mre5.geojson
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type_map"

JALAN
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

